%% Diagram: Message Lifecycle State Machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> COMPOSING: user types

    COMPOSING --> PENDING: send (client UUID)
    note right of PENDING
        local optimistic insert
        retried with same messageId
    end note

    PENDING --> SENT: server seq + persist
    PENDING --> FAILED: ws closed + retry exhausted

    SENT --> DELIVERED: recipient gateway acks
    SENT --> QUEUED_PUSH: recipient offline
    QUEUED_PUSH --> DELIVERED: APNs/FCM ack
    QUEUED_PUSH --> EXPIRED: TTL elapsed

    DELIVERED --> READ: recipient reads
    READ --> [*]

    FAILED --> PENDING: user retries
    FAILED --> [*]: dropped
    EXPIRED --> [*]
